                        <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" type="supplied" key="person_f7123">Fayz̤ Allāh Anṣārī Jawnpūrī "Himmat"</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="per" key="person_f7123" type="supplied">فيض الله انصارى همّت</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="work_21941">Intikhāb-i haft iqlīm</title>
                     <title xml:lang="per" key="work_21941">انتخاب هفت اقليم</title>
                     <note>
                        <p>Althernative title: <title>Muntakhab-i haft iqlīm</title>
                        </p>
                        <p>Althernative title: <title>Ḥālāt-i Jawnpūr</title>
                        </p>
                        <name />
                        <p>Abridgement of the Timurid or Mughal-period geographical history, <title>Haft iqlīm </title>of <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="person_232008283" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/232008283" role="aut">Amīn ibn Aḥmad Rāzī,</persName> at the request of Lālah Rām Dayāl (the qānūn-gū of Jaunpur), made in regnal year 24 of Emperor Shāh ʿĀlam, 1196/1782
                        </p>
                        <p>Excerpts, consisting of preface and portion on history of Jaunpur under the Sharqī Sulṭān dynasty</p>
                        <p>Preface additionally based on another local history, the Mirʾāt al-asrār (author unnamed)</p>
                        <p>Version of preface differs from another BL copy of the manuscript dedicated to Vajīh al-Dīn ʿAlī Khān (Ethé 727)</p>
                        <p>Not dated</p>
                     </note>
